      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published FDA pump experimental measurements across 5 operating points. Mean relative error 8.3%; all predictions within experimental uncertainty band. UQ campaign (Latin hypercube, n=512) with Sobol sensitivity indices computed for inlet flow rate, rotational speed, and blood viscosity; rotational speed accounts for 61% of NIH variance. Acceptance criterion RH < 1 satisfied at all operating conditions."
    },
