    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 guidance. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predicts NIH within 15% of experimental measurements across the CPB operating envelope. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 satisfied at all operating points. UQ campaign results (documented in validation evidence record VR-01) confirm rotational speed as dominant uncertainty driver; this information was incorporated into the assessment of the model inputs factor. The credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device hemolysis claim.",
